      <div id="columns">
      <h1> The right to work, right to serve </h1>
      <p><q>Nobody expected much from women in work or in socity because all the expectations were about home and family responsibilities.</q></p>
      
      <h2>The right of equal pay</h2>
      <p><q>I believe in equal pay and carry my own things.</q></p>
      
      <h2>Steve's secrets of success</h2>
      <p><q>always surround yourself with first-rate people and people that you like and that don't mean people like you and choose partners very carefully.</q></p>
      <p><q>work is not just something I do when I'd rather be doing something else and there is a beauty in work when we do it properly and in humility</q></p>
          
    </main>
      <div>
        <h1 id="joy">Joy of work</h1>
    <p><b>Find something you really care about, <br>get trained,<br> sourround yourself with first class people<br>and then enjoy.</b></p>
         
